I did not know that our government had such a good sense of humour. Did you hear the joke they dropped earlier this week? At a media briefing, Eskom told South Africa there would be no more load-shedding if all went to plan. They were a bit late for April Fools’ Day, but I am sure many still appreciated the laugh. Here are this week’s tech deals. Enjoy. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301852" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301854" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301856" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-3.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-3.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-3-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-3-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301858" src="h